  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Market Development: The Project will help create market alternatives for Asian based primary insurance companies which are today dependent on European or North American based reinsurance groups or inadequate local, nationally based reinsurers.  As an Asian based reinsurer, Clipper aims to differentiate itself from established multinational reinsurance companies in terms of its pricing and capital allocation, and also avoid the often inadequate portfolio diversification found in single-country reinsurance companies.      Local Capacity Enhancement: In partnership with local primary market operators, the Project will improve the availability of technical expertise and reinsurance underwriting capacity in key product areas such a micro-insurance, natural catastrophe and agricultural crop insurance.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Peak Reinsurance Company Limited (Peak Re or the Company), owned 100% by Peak Reinsurance Holdings Ltd. (PeakRe Holidngs), is a newly established reinsurance company, headquartered in Hong Kong SAR, China and operates across Asia.</narrative>
